nodes.text: When the Khormai warlord Unger Gout struck a deal with the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars, a resistance movement sprung up to oppose him. The resistance, led at least in part by the Khormai Adaroo, joined forced with a Galactic Republic force under the leadership of the Jedi Masters Kit Fisto and Plo Koon to drive Gout and the Separatists from the planet Khorm.
